": "https://scontent-sin11-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974804_434893712966828_3854371421829702601_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ABF5yZ69tn0Q7kNvgFqhCES&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin11-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDF2XRsQD3bD0QicwcmW-rfn7vjYfwcaIFqM04ukDbsoQ&oe=677E7234"}]}, "id": "27493630556918928", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "FinalProduct (1) (1).png", "id": "567283012523806", "uri": "https://scontent-sin6-3.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974439_567283015857139_4471720054865289592_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=m9B8-D4-OIIQ7kNvgFQbI2d&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-3.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAxEc54vvcGY5lLgVz0MDFCon3u48Q1CqQvZm009xLHKg&oe=677E5B9E"}, {"file_name": "Spawn (1) (1).png", "id": "487640170923746", "uri": "https://scontent-sin2-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031339_487640174257079_4205197844445410285_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=l2Mr_I6IrdwQ7kNvgHr3avZ&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin2-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBOcqIjekdHbPNvjIAWtAwzNyA8kSzFEjcwQ_oBsKibgg&oe=677E6EC2"}, {"file_name": "MikeRing (1) (1).png", "id": "1104907238013447", "uri": "https://scontent-sin11-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031551_1104907241346780_2679845581644232202_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=GcZMdVsLG_4Q7kNvgECsOH_&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin11-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD49hHEJ5OxpvdWAf669G2W7JorHHrUbvPkTUFTGDFEtA&oe=677E4D8E"}, {"file_name": "HalloweenSneak5 (1).png", "id": "1573950076564522", "uri": "https://scontent-sin6-4.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974854_1573950079897855_5936192113943480356_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=5wazbwvSjsgQ7kNvgGBOurz&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-4.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBXOhf2OtH75XJ1gZvkZZ9BUQPl0b04Ww-Jlo1s4uJ2FQ&oe=677E6B44"}, {"file_name": "Training2 (1).png", "id": "993997169161194", "uri": "https://scontent-sin6-3.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974900_993997172494527_3748398888020150400_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=fPJEBJXjf-IQ7kNvgFRAsmv&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-3.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD6thVRBEQCr3Hgw2ws9tcr6oSIr0Uy_N5JxNT1FCvafg&oe=677E6BEE"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Virtual Knockout", "keywords": ["Boxing", "VK", "Virtual", "Knockout", "Box"], "long_description": "### Virtual Knockout \n\nStep into the ring with **Virtual Knockout** the ultimate free VR multiplayer boxing game. Whether you're a beginner or a seasoned boxer, VK offers an immersive and exhilarating experience.\n\n**Features:**\n\n- **Multiplayer Mode**: \n  - **Public Lobbies**: Spar with players worldwide in exciting, competitive matches.\n  - **Private Lobbies**: Practice and compete with friends or selected opponents in a controlled environment.\n\n- **Training Arenas**:\n  - **Public Training**: Join sessions to learn new techniques and improve skills collectively.\n  - **Private Training**: Train solo or with a coach, focusing on specific areas like speed, power, or defense.\n\n- **Realistic Boxing Mechanics**:\n  - **True-to-Life Movements**: Experience authentic boxing with advanced motion tracking.\n  - **Dynamic Environments**: Fight in various arenas, each with a unique atmosphere and challenges.\n\n- **Customization and Progression**:\n  - **Avatar Customization**: Personalize your fighter with a wide range of options.\n  - **Skill Progression**: Track your progress, earn achievements, and climb the ranks.\n\nPrepare to enter the ring and prove your skills with Virtual Knockout!", "short_description": "Welcome to the first ever Free Quest Multiplayer Boxing Game! Join public or private lobbies and brawl!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://docs.google.com/document/d/16nVx6NY4obMdecDeanQVyuQt7YWvr4kuDTn19ccpQ0U/edit?usp=sharing", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Phoze", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://docs.google.com/document/d/1YkGs89urCk65xODWdYlGF4bFnXxgmVktcYsBFWT